gildan activewear inc gilto company profile  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile gildan activewear inc gilto related topics stocksstock screenerapparel  accessories overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse gilto on toronto stock exchange cad am edt change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description gildan activewear inc incorporated on may   is a manufacturer and marketer of branded basic family apparel including tshirts fleece sport shirts underwear socks hosiery and shapewear the company operates through two segments printwear and branded apparel the company sells its products under various brands including the gildan gold toe anvil comfort colors american apparel alstyle secret silks kushyfoot secret silky therapy plus peds and medipeds brands the company also distributes some of its sock products through its the united states sock license for the under armour brand and it also markets an array of products through a global license for the mossy oak brand the companys products are sold in the printwear and retail markets the company distributes its products in printwear markets in the united states canada mexico europe asiapacific and latin america in retail markets the company sells its products to a range of retailers primarily in the united states and canada and it also manufactures for global athletic and lifestyle consumer brandsprintwearthe printwear segment designs manufactures sources markets and distributes undecorated activewear products the company mainly sells undecorated activewear products blanks primarily to wholesale distributors who sell its products to screenprinters advertising specialty distributors and embroiderers who in turn decorate the products with designs and logos and sells the imprinted activewear into a range of enduse markets these include educational institutions athletic dealers event merchandisers promotional product distributors charitable organizations entertainment promoters travel and tourism venues and retailers its activewear products are used in a range of daily activities by individuals and have various applications including work and school uniforms and athletic team wear and for various other purposes to convey individual group and team identity its primary brands include gildan gildan performance anvil comfort colors american apparel alstyle and new balancebranded apparelthe branded apparel segment designs manufactures sources markets and distributes branded family apparel which includes athletic casual and dress socks underwear activewear sheer hosiery legwear and shapewear products which are sold to retailers in the united states and canada the company markets its products primarily under its companyowned and licensed brands its primary products include socks underwear activewear athletic socks legwear foot solutions and sheerpantyhose its primary brands include gildan platinum smart basics g powersox silver toe signature gold by goldtoe and all prothe company competes with berkshire hathaway inc hanesbrands inc delta apparel inc color image apparel inc next level apparel bella  canvas garan incorporated renfro corporation jockey international inc kayser roth corporation and spanx inc » full overview of gilto company address gildan activewear inc rd  de maisonneuve blvd w montreal   qc   ha j p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation william anderson  glenn chamandy  rhodri harries  michael hoffman  eric lehman  » more officers  directors gildan activewear inc news » more gilto news related topics stocksstock screenerapparel  accessories gildan activewear srl  welcome to mygildancom choose your location usa english español canada english français europe english français deutsch japan  english australia english mexico esp